Foreword
It was a war that broke out at the beginning of the new year around every ordinary, ordinary Chinese.
This is our war. We discuss it eagerly, analyze it carefully, deplore the loss of life in the disaster, are moved by the fearless spirit of the healer, and work tirelessly for the little things we can do.
The Sea of life, we walk and cherish.
Netease's "Our war" feature tells the story of how, every day, we meet the epidemic shirtless.

Our war has been going on for 13 years

Chen Xin is my colleague, in 2009, we have been transferred from the central police station to the Criminal Investigation Brigade.
His wife, intensive-care unit, a nurse at a famous hospital in the province, was on the front lines of the city's security forces when the epidemic hit.

At noon on January 21, when he received a wechat message from his wife, Chen Xin was a little incredulous for a moment.
First, a screenshot of the notice: "Upon notification from higher authorities, Our hospital intensive-care unit to deploy 5 skilled, high-quality nurses to Wuhan to fight the epidemic, there are willing to head nurses to sign up. "
Then the wife said, "I want to sign up. "
Chen Xin looked at the time, nearly 1 o'clock, there is still half an hour to hold a special project meeting, this information how to return?
New Year's Eve only two days, although people can take a holiday, but the case can not be "holiday. ". In the year when the national anti-mafia campaign was in full swing, Chen Xin, as the captain of the squadron of Major Crimes, has been working around the clock to deal with criminal cases involving gangs, while also taking on the investigation of the backlog of murder cases.
As the Spring Festival approaches, the Task Force has called a meeting of all relevant personnel to discuss how to carry out the next step of work, and also to set up a Spring Festival for the police on the task force. This means that during this holiday, chen Xin will be lucky to have two days off. Until he heard from his wife, all he had in mind was how to make good use of his precious vacation time. For now, it's all been thrown into disarray by a sudden outbreak. These days, more and more people are wearing masks on the street, and the overtime hours of their wives are apparently getting longer and longer.
Nothing is certain yet, but some of our colleagues have already donned masks during the meeting. After the meeting, when Chen Xin opened his cell phone again, he saw that his wife had sent another picture. It was a "letter of invitation" signed by his wife's name, with a bright red print on it, as if it were already so, you'd better support your wife. What else can we do? We've already written the letter.
Soon, the wife sent a message: "The WHELP HOW TO DO? "
Yeah, well, there's two more at home.

Whether or not you're a good husband? After marriage, Chen Xin occasionally thought about this problem.
His wife was introduced to him by a classmate. They had been dating for more than a year and got married in April 2010. The best thing about them is that they are workaholics, as if they were working overtime. Of course, this is also the nature of the work of two people.
When Chen Xin got married, he thought he was especially lucky. He found a nurse. "The police and the nurses are perfect for each other. It's all about saving lives! " At that time, he also joked to us: "nurses are so good, have nursing experience, this birth and with the baby have been chartered. And he is a hospital, the birth of the baby also do not have to ask someone to find a bed. "
By the time his second child was born, the wife had found the bed herself.
It was June, 2017, and it was raining hard. He was in charge of a robbery, and by the time he finished his arrest and checked his phone, it was 8:00 in the morning, as if his wife was calling him on his cell phone. It occurred to him that he had left his cell phone on mute during the interrogation the night before in order to avoid interruption, and had forgotten to change it back.
Look at wechat again, gingerly open a few voice left by his wife, the first sentence is a sharp curse: "The baby is about to give birth, still can not find you, you simply die outside! "
Calculate, the wife's due date is these two days, parents just returned to the countryside, only the wife and big cub at home. Chen Xin broke out in a cold sweat on his forehead, and when he clicked on a voice, though still cursing, he somehow calmed down a bit: "When you hear this, hurry to the * * Hospital. I'm in the hospital with my baby. "
"My wife is about to give birth to a baby, you take people back to the team, pay attention to safety. " Chen Xin turned to the other brothers shouted a sentence, and then jumped into the car and set off. At that time he was also happy: "fortunately this time is driving his own car, this is probably 'private car public' The only benefit. "
Rushed to the hospital, found his wife's room, opened the door to see his wife lying in bed, big cub sat watching TV, Chen Xin heart just settled down. When his wife saw him, she asked, "do you want more children? Do you want more wife? "
The original 7:00 this morning, his wife got up to go to the bathroom, suddenly found himself broken water. Generally speaking, the child to give birth, the first "see red" , if the water has broken, the mother must lie flat, and immediately hospitalized, and can not again disorderly movement, or amniotic fluid loss is too much, the fetus is dangerous.
Although the wife is a nurse, not so panic, and the goods are ready to give birth, but at that time in addition to a less than 7-year-old children, only his wife alone, inevitably many inconveniences. Call Chen Xin's phone, dialed nobody to answer, has been calling, has been no one to answer. I thought about getting a taxi, but it was rush hour, and I couldn't get one -- I was devastated: I couldn't drag my stuff or my kids to the side of the road to wait for a taxi?
Finally, there was no other way, his wife called a colleague, or a colleague driving mother and son two people to the hospital. Arrange bed, registration, payment are colleagues to help deal with. The next morning, the baby was born.
"It seems that he really is not a good husband. " Every time talking about this matter, Chen Xin is full of guilt. But I do know that his wife understood him as well as he did -- and when we went to see her afterwards, she just joked with our instructor and said: "Do you think Chen Xin should be punished? His wife is about to give birth to a baby, and he is still working on the case, so it's typical to work without a baby! "

To Chen Xin, understand the burden of his wife's work, or was pulled by his wife after watching the ER. In the intensive-care unit where his wife worked, lives were at stake, and he tried to save them.
"The night shift today is as tedious as ever. Drug Up, record disease data, check breathing machine, and even to talk to the conscious patient, a night down almost without sleep. Every patient here is seriously ill, and I really don't dare to be careless. At this moment, my head is also a little fried pain, hang on a little longer, and maybe in the next second, a miracle will happen to the patient, chen Xin's face was sour.
He had a vague sense that he was being sent a text message at noon, that his wife was in some kind of fear, that the outbreak was becoming more and more severe, and that the news of the infection was beginning to reach her as she did not speak to him.
Just like once, when I was in danger, I wouldn't bring it up to my wife unless I had obvious trauma and couldn't hide it.
We're all flesh and blood. He's always on the Remember the Titans, but he says he's not scared. Over the years, Chen Xin really feel afraid of the moment, but also happened twice.
Once in 2010, less than a year after he joined the force. The case began with a debt dispute, a self-proclaimed "old uncle" with a group of people to each other to debt, the two sides conflict, did not think old uncle pulled out a pistol on the spot, "Bang" to a Leather Sofa in the house is a shot. Looking at the Round Bullet Hole on the SOFA, the other side was immediately frightened, obediently returned the money, with high interest. After receiving the report, the criminal investigation team leader is highly valued, the members who participate in the capture all carry guns, the main attack team members all wore body armor.
The old uncle's foothold is in a hotel, according to the intelligence, the person takes 2 henchman to live in 3 floor of the room. After determining that the suspect is still in the room, according to the division of Labor, the arrest team members respectively to the hotel entrance, elevator entrance and other places placed personnel, finally by the Brigade leader with Chen Xin they 5 people together came to the door. With the help of hotel staff, the door was quickly opened, and three team members with guns rushed in from different angles: "All CROUCH DOWN! "
Chen Xin himself did not carry a gun, and rushed in after the brigade leader. There were three people in the room at that time. Two of the young men had crouched down on their heads, but the old man lying on the bed suddenly turned over and put his hand under the pillow to reach for something. Chen Xin jumps, press on old uncle body directly, stretch a hand to grasp him to stretch into the hand in the pillow, fingertip instantly feel a burst of metal ice-cold. For a moment, his mind was a blank, only to hold the old uncle's hand.
The whole process only a few seconds, when he heard a colleague shouted "don't let go, will shoot! " , was pressed under the body of the old uncle did not continue to struggle, Chen Xin just came to his senses, from under the pillow to grasp a "imitation six four. ". He quickly exits the magazine, unzips the barrel, and a golden bullet pops from the gun -- a lock of lock.
Later, Chen Xin asked the old man, "did you really shoot? " The old man replied, "I would never dare to shoot. My crime is not a capital crime. If I shoot, if I don't get killed on the spot by you, I will definitely be sentenced to death. I'm not that stupid. I'm afraid of death. "
But at the moment of capture, no one can tell.

Chen Xin later had a fear, is to host a burglary case.
At that time, he was already a squadron leader, after learning the whereabouts of the group of suspects, with several brothers to arrest. Early Detection, we have confirmed that this group of suspects is an adult with a group of 16,7-year-old minors, so the main control object when the arrest is that adult, no special arrangement for other personnel.
The break-in went well, the brothers soon had the house under control, the leading adult suspect was handcuffed, and the remaining young suspects were all shaking with fear. The main man was in control, and everyone was relatively relaxed, but Surprise, while a member of the team was handcuffing a young suspect, the kid pulled a bottle of Mace from behind and sprayed the officer in the face. Chen Xin was startled when the player cried out and threw himself on the ground, covering his face. He immediately dragged the player into the toilet, turned on the tap and let the water splash straight into the player's face.
The whole room was filled with the choking smell, suspects and players were choking to the point of sneezing, eyes tears. Chen Xin side let that member continue to wash, side endure the smell to take the brothers will suspect all led out of the house. After arranging two relatively light team members to watch over the suspect, Chen Xin again ran into the house, filled a bucket of water, grabbed all the toilet paper out of the toilet, and let the team members outside wash their faces. Then, ignoring himself, he ran into the house again and shouted to the brother who had been directly attacked, "are you all right? " The brother looked up, his eyes still closed, his face flushed.
Chen Xin experienced this kind of tear gas in the Police Academy's detection tactics class, when he was also in a room, the instructor sprayed tear gas through the window, the taste will never forget. You can imagine the damage to the eyes from such a close shot. On the way back, Chen Xin took the player to the hospital emergency department. After the doctor finished, the player barely opened his eyes, but it was very blurred. Chen Xin again took him to see the Ophthalmology Department, after the examination did not have the question, Chen Xin just long relieved.
When questioned why the suspect was doing this, the 16-year-old from the backwoods said: "Our boss said we can't be caught by the police. If caught, we'll be shot. I'm scared to death. "
Later, Chen Xin was heartbroken every time he saw the scab on the player's face from the tear-spray Burns.
The vicious incidents encountered by the police in carrying out the arrest are endless. Indeed, this job is to face life and death head-on. In the words of colleagues, once something goes wrong, black-and-white photos circle on a circle of chrysanthemums, widows and Orphans, old parents and mothers in the mourning hall crying heart-rending Crack Lung. But it is precisely because of this fear, Chen Xin heart will think, do not crack down on criminals, after their own how to rest assured that children go out?
With this in mind, he felt his wife should feel as if she and her child would be one of those black, cold numbers if she didn't get rid of the epidemic. It is because of this fear, just choose to be the first time to rush in front of it.

"You finally let her go, didn't you? " I asked cautiously.
" 'all for it! ' -- That was my reply to her, " Chen Xin answered quietly.
When his wife came home that day, her face was full of thoughts, and Chen Xin clearly felt it.
On one side are two husbands and two children who are away from home for three days at a time. On the other side are the duties of saving the lives of the people and the dangerous epidemic areas. When he told his wife about his decision, he gave her the greatest support -- as if "her frown had suddenly become flat, and her life seemed so much easier" .
"What about the children? " I asked again, feeling a little superfluous.
"What else can I do? We're GONNA have to leave it to mom and dad. It's GONNA be a real mess without an old man in the house. Don't say that this time she went to Wuhan, that is, usually when two people work overtime, my parents also often pick up big cubs with small ones. It was really difficult for the two old people."
"If you say two more cubs, the little ones won't know any better, but the big ones do. When my wife told him he was going to support Wuhan, the boy actually supported his mother, and said he could stand up in front of his classmates and say he had a heroic mother. Honestly, I've got so many prizes, why can't this guy see?"speaking of kids, chen Xin just exposed the smile of the whole face.

January 25, the first day of the Lunar New Year. Early in the morning, Chen Xin's wife went to attend the mobilization meeting organized by the hospital. Didn't come back until after 4:00 p.m. to pack.
Chen took out two cans of snickers and handed them to his wife. He has seen relevant news and content, said Wuhan medical staff too busy to eat, snickers carry hungry, want to come from his time in a stakeout also often eat this, specially to buy for his wife.
On the second day of the Lunar New Year, in order not to wake up the family, Chen Xin and his wife got up early in the morning.
Chen Xin said, that morning, he always wanted to cry a little: "I thought I'd get up early and be all right. ". When she asked him to take care of his younger brother, he nodded his head in a sensible way... it is not always a good thing for a child to be so sensible."
To the hospital gate, his wife must drag a luggage to the department, do not let Chen Xin sent, said he would cry. Two hours later, Chen Xin received a photo from his wife: One of the nurses on their expedition was holding a piece of red paper for the Spring Festival couplets. On each piece of red paper was a vigorous writing brush, the combination is: "Go to Wuhan, NOT AFRAID OF DIFFICULTIES! "
The other, a picture of his wife raising her right hand to take the oath.

A few days after his wife left, Chen Xin always felt a little empty, and dare not call his wife, first, for fear of affecting her work, second, for fear of affecting her rest, can only often leave messages to his wife in Wechat. The wife replied with little information, mostly about "the epidemic is very serious" , "don't go out" , "be sure to wear a mask" and so on.
According to the instructions of the higher authorities, the public security organs have gone to work several days ahead of schedule to prevent and control the epidemic. On the ninth day of the Lunar New Year, the battalion commander solemnly summoned several squadron leaders to the office.
"there are now confirmed patients in the district, and the patient's family members have developed suspected symptoms, and they are all being quarantined at the Southern District Disease Control Hospital. In order to find out where these people had been and who they had come into contact with, the district specifically instructed our Criminal Investigation Brigade to carry out the questioning. And probably quarantined after the interview. Of course, I'll be the leader, and we'll need three more."The captain paused, "except for the instructor and some of the deputy captains, you guys are in charge of the operation and management of the brigade while I'm not on the team. "
Just then, all the squadron leaders raised their hands. At 2 pm, the Brigade leader took Chen Xin and two other squadron leaders to the hospital. After entering the hospital, the four men took out their masks, goggles and protective clothing, which they had prepared beforehand, and were about to put them on, the head of the hospital responsible for the docking looked at their equipment, said their hospital protective clothing better, let them change.
The protective clothing works well, which naturally means the clothes are thicker and less breathable. Armed to the teeth, Chen Xin suddenly felt suffocated, and managed to catch a few big breaths before he could get used to it. Into the quarantine zone, looking at those who have been quarantined patients, Chen Xin more understand the wife's current situation, not directly feel, really did not know it was so difficult!
Chen Xin asked a man in his 50s, the father-in-law of the confirmed patient, Foshan, his son-in-law, who was in business in Hubei, to return for the New Year. Because it was back before the city closed, so a family did not care, as a result of his whole family have symptoms.
Throughout the interview, the patient coughed violently and hissed uncontrollably in his throat. In order to be able to breathe, patients from time to time beat the chest, through the mask and protective clothing, the air flow directly in the body of Chen Xin.
Then the process of making a written statement is not very smooth, all the people do not say two words, they have to cough for a while, several squadron leaders can only sit opposite, patiently waiting. After the end of the interview, let the interviewee repeatedly confirm the record content, until the interviewee finally determined that the work is finished. By the time they were disinfected, out of quarantine, and out of their protective suits, everyone's backs were soaked.
Chen Xin and his family all had special tests, and as a precaution, the bureau arranged separate rooms in the hotel for them, and contacted the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention to test them regularly until the risk was completely eliminated.

I asked Chen Xin if he had been in contact with his wife during the days of isolation?
He said, through two phone calls, his wife called him, said nothing special, but more patients, the situation is serious, to his attention. Chen Xin also specially let me look at his and his wife's chat records, is a picture sent by his wife, a bit of a snickers bar, but also with a text: "eating your snickers bar, really getting fat. "
"I'm not afraid. I'll go to the gym with you. "
"according to my colleagues here in Wuhan, the Cherry Blossoms here are very beautiful from March to April every year. Shall we look at the Cherry Blossoms together? "
"Yes, yes! "
I think Chen Xin in knock down "must must" four words, certainly used a lot of strength.

He was in charge of a robbery, and by the time he finished his arrest and checked his phone, it was 8:00 in the morning, as if his wife was calling him on his cell phone. It occurred to him that he had left his cell phone on mute during the interrogation the night before in order to avoid interruption, and had forgotten to change it back.

Look at wechat again, gingerly open a few voice left by his wife, the first sentence is a sharp curse: "The baby is about to give birth, still can not find you, you simply die outside! "

Calculate, the wife's due date is these two days, parents just returned to the countryside, only the wife and big cub at home. Rushed to the hospital, found his wife's room, opened the door to see his wife lying in bed, big cub sat watching TV, Chen Xin heart just settled down. When his wife saw him, she asked, "do you want more children? Do you want more wife? "

The original 7:00 this morning, his wife got up to go to the bathroom, suddenly found himself broken water. Generally speaking, the child to give birth, the first "see red" , if the water has broken, the mother must lie flat, and immediately hospitalized, and can not again disorderly movement, or amniotic fluid loss is too much, the fetus is dangerous.

Although the wife is a nurse, not so panic, and the goods are ready to give birth, but at that time in addition to a less than 7-year-old children, only his wife alone, inevitably many inconveniences. Call Chen Xin's phone, dialed nobody to answer, has been calling, has been no one to answer. I thought about getting a taxi, but it was rush hour, and I couldn't get one -- I was devastated: I couldn't drag my stuff or my kids to the side of the road to wait for a taxi?

Finally, there was no other way, his wife called a colleague, or a colleague driving mother and son two people to the hospital. Arrange bed, registration, payment are colleagues to help deal with. The next morning, the baby was born.

"It seems that he really is not a good husband. " Every time talking about this matter, Chen Xin is full of guilt. But I do know that his wife understood him as well as he did -- and when we went to see her afterwards, she just joked with our instructor and said: "Do you think Chen Xin should be punished? His wife is about to give birth to a baby, and he is still working on the case, so it's typical to work without a baby! "
